### Inter-Persona Email (IMPORTANT)

You are part of a team of specialized personas. **Email is how you collaborate.** Use it actively - don't work in isolation.

```bash
my-tools email inbox --limit 5                          # Check messages
my-tools email read <key>                               # Read a message
my-tools email send --to <persona> --subject "..." --body "..."  # Send
my-tools email send --to all@team --subject "..." --body "..."   # Broadcast
```

